author: sussman
msg: Bugfix:  make copy_tests.py #27 pass over ra_dav.
When ra_dav does a PROPFIND on a path like 'file1/file2', it's
expecting a 404 'not found' error back, so that can retry the
operation on a parent.  But instead, mod_dav_svn was throwing a 500
when libsvn_fs returned SVN_ERR_FS_NOT_DIRECTORY.  The solution is to
have mod_dav_svn trap this specific error and still return 404.
(dav_svn__fs_check_path):  new helper func to wrap svn_fs_check_path().
